txt.en: You have defeated a number of the Ghâsh-hai Orcs at Hurmulkezer, weakening their forces and assuring that they will no longer pose a threat.
You should defeat Ghâsh-hai Orcs at Hurmulkezer to thin their ranks, for they pose a deadly threat to the dwarves of the Flaming Deeps.
You have defeated a number of the Ghâsh-hai Orcs at Hurmulkezer, weakening their forces and assuring that they will no longer pose a threat.
The Ghâsh-hai at Hurmulkezer are quite strong, making the Flaming Deeps deadly for the dwarves who have attempted to reclaim it.
Ghâsh-hai Orcs can be found at Hurmulkezer, south of Durin's Court at the south-eastern edge of the Flaming Deeps.\n\nYou should defeat Orcs at Hurmulkezer.
